The restaurant has just been renewed after my previous visit. The new decor looks more elegant and brighter. The tea is fragrant, the drinks are normal. Everything seemed fine until I took the car out. Because I arrived at rush hour, I couldn't pull up to the curb in front of the restaurant to park my car. So I went around the bow of the ship to park my car at the back of the shop. At that time, I saw a number of motorbikes parked there. But it turned out it was a customer's car from the restaurant next door, and I don't understand why they were allowed to park their car on this side of the restaurant. And when I took my car out, I saw that my car was parked close to that shop's car, blocking the helmet I hung on the car. When I took the hat out, it was completely scratched like the photo below. The car was parked close to me and I had to struggle for a while to get it out. Why do other shops in Trung Nguyen's area leave their cars indiscriminately like that, leading to damage to customers' belongings and cars? If Trung Nguyen guests are not allowed to park there, there must be a warning sign to let guests know!
The restaurant space is clean and cool. Enthusiastic and attentive service staff. Drinks that suit your taste. Will come back if I have a chance.

The small space of the restaurant looks cozy and has a diverse menu. The brand is famous but the menu prices are ok. Come here to meet deadlines and carefreely, the staff constantly refills tea. The tea here is quite fragrant. One thing I really like is that soft music is played here, making it easy to concentrate

I really like drinking Trung Nguyen filter coffee, but when I go to Nguyen Thuet to drink it, I don't know what kind of coffee to use or how you guys make it, but it's very bad: neither fragrant nor strong and bitter and not as delicious as other places. Another Trung Nguyen Legend! - The restaurant space is extremely hot and sometimes the toilet smells bad! The whole shop has an air conditioner, but it's very old and not cool. It's so hot that you have to turn on the fan to drink, which is like torture! I don't think a big brand would leave a restaurant that old and hot like that, but the air conditioner is so old and black that it's not cold enough! This restaurant would rather be closed than leave it as it will lose its image! Not a single piece! After drinking, Beo and Nga said goodbye and won't go back! And they also don't want to go back to any Trung Nguyen shop to drink again! Someone went to the shop's Facebook page to talk about this and only looked at it and didn't respond to customers, which is really bad customer service! The shop staff's face is not happy either!
